    <!--
     Fix white status bar during Action Mode.

     Overrides the colors used by the AppCompat DecorView to prevent a solid status bar guard.
     Otherwise, selecting multiple items (e.g., selecting multiple Drafts in DraftsActivity)
     makes the statusbar appear white.

     Lint flags this as unused, which needs to be ignored.
